"Projections series, analysed in the ILO&apos;s World Employment and Social "
"Outlook reports. For more information, on the model used to derive these "
"estimates, refer to the ILO paper &#x201C;Employment and economic class in "
"the developing world&#x201D; (Kapsos and Bourmpoula, 2013), available at <a "
"href=\"http://www.ilo.org/wcmsp5/groups/public/---dgreports/---inst/"
"documents/publication/wcms_216451.pdf\">http://www.ilo.org/wcmsp5/groups/"
